---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
import logo from "../../public/logo.png";
---

<Base>
	<img
		src={logo.src}
		alt="Glass Tongue Logo"
		class="w-4/5 max-w-sm mx-auto"
	/>

	<div class="text-red-600 text-lg leading-snug">
		a fracture in sound<br />
		nothing has dropped yet — but it’s coming
	</div>

	<div class="text-gray-500 text-base space-y-4">
		<p>Glass Tongue is emotional brutality: poetic, guttural, surreal.</p>
		<p>
			Formed to answer the question no one asked: <br
				class="md:hidden"
			/><em>“What if Cannibal Corpse covered Owl City?”</em>
		</p>
	</div>

	<footer class="text-gray-500 text-sm">
		<p>📧 contact@glasstongue.com</p>
		<p>© 2025 Glass Tongue — All rights shattered.</p>
	</footer>
</Base>
